&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="../application/views/involved/img/upload/032.jpg"><img src="http://www.dur.ac.uk/butler.jcr/application/views/involved/img/upload/032.jpg"><br /><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%;"><br /></span><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;">Butler R&amp;A Soc. is an open and friendly society for anyone who enjoys listening to rock and alternative music, including (but by no means limited to!): classic rock, motown, folk, grunge, punk, metal, funk, ska, hip-hop, emo, drum and bass/electro, indie…basically, anything you wouldn't tend to hear on a typical night out.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;<br />We host a night&nbsp;in one of Durham’s best alternative music venues, Fishtank, on a regular basis. During the night, members of the society DJ for half an hour each and play a wide variety of music - so there’s sure to be something you’ll love!&nbsp;We especially encourage freshers to get involved in Fishtank nights. It doesn’t take long to learn the ropes, and once you do, those nights will fast become what you look forward to during the week and definitely remember fondly for a long time afterwards.<br /><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"></span>&nbsp;<br /><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"></span>We also&nbsp;organise&nbsp;nights out to some of Newcastle's rock and alternative clubs, as well as having themed R&amp;A socials and nights out to Durham’s best alternative venues.&nbsp;We usually have a few casual house/flat party socials and bar crawls during the year which feature our infamous Rock Soc. cocktail, and live band events at both Fishtank and Butler.<br />&nbsp;<br /><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;"></span>This year is looking to be a good one for Butler R&amp;A, and we look forward to welcoming new members into one of Butler’s best societies!</span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB">&nbsp;\m/</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; line-height: normal;"><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"><br /></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal"><br /><strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"></span></strong><span style="font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB"></span></p>